    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@U01JNTE35QS> definitely some interesting challenges! On the robotics side testing anything that interacts with the physical world can be tricky. \n\nOn the biology side things there is lots exciting happening. Imagine trying to program and debug a computer that you are still in the process of reverse engineering to figure out the instruction set and operating principles. Its a real fun mix of engineering combined with pure science, and it requires new tools to be invented to do the work :-)",
